name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 9, a blogger lamented the depression of Yiwu after a field visit.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: At present, universities around San Francisco are still working hard to recruit people to welcome Xi Jinping's visit.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: At the same time, the embassy also emphasized that it was important to highlight that this was a voluntary act by the students and not to highlight or involve the embassy.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Oh, and you can’t mention Xi Jinping’s name, you can only say “national leader”

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 9, a doctor questioned Zhongshan Second Hospital’s behavior of dismantling the laboratory after a group of students were diagnosed with cancer on Weibo. He then said that he “received a call”

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Netizens made a video to satirize the incident of Zhongshan Second Hospital students suffering from cancer

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: In a Zhihu post about how to view the mother of the murdered child being threatened with the job of a public official at home after the collapse of the Jiamusi Stadium, another Shandong woman who was similarly threatened shared her experience.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 7, Nanjing Jiangning Urban Construction requested a trust company to refund part of the fees that were higher than the annual loan reference interest ten years ago on the grounds of "recovering stolen money and compensating for losses."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On November 9, media reported that Moore's Thread, a domestic GPU company, laid off employees at a lightning speed after being sanctioned by the United States, and the compensation plan was far below the industry average, causing dissatisfaction among employees.
It is said that the employees' requests for help and complaints on the Internet have all been deleted.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:

Following Hunan Satellite TV’s launch of “Marx Meets Confucius”

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On November 8, the media revealed that many people in Puyang, Henan reported that the mortgage loans they applied for were actually consumer loans.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On Xiaohongshu, a netizen said that when he took a taxi in Beijing, the driver posted a reminder on the passenger seat saying "Recording, please do not chat"

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Just now, the meeting time between the Chinese and American heads of state was determined. From November 14 to 17, Xi Jinping will travel to San Francisco to meet with Biden and attend the APEC Leaders' Informal Meeting.
